> * Carnage narrowed her optics as she lowered her gun and placed it back in
it's hold, what had just happened? First this bot drops by and says that he
has to protect Teltoli, then these other two bots come along and a shoot out
breaks out, then they all disappear! This either had a good plan behind it
or it was all very stupid!
> She looked at the smooth surface of the lake as it reflected her image
back to her, what had just happened was very strange. She shrugged, but life
went on.
> Carnage turned to Teltoli but didn't say anything, she also looked Tritan
over for strength...sizeing him up.
> She growled, for some reason she just didn't seem to like him. He was an
Alliance member for one thing and frankly that was all she needed, she
didn't give a nano if he said that he wasn't like the others the fact still
remained.
> Carnage crossed her arms and looked over at Teltoli, she gave her a look
that mainly said that words were words and nothing more, don't trust
everybot!*
